data.title: Sec 0917
data.meta_description: Sec 0917 - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document is a roll of successful examinees for the Licensure Examination for Teachers - Secondary held on September 24, 2017. It lists the sequence numbers and names of the first 163 examinees who passed the exam. The document provides the date the exam was held, when the results were released, and indicates it is page 2 of 994 pages documenting all the successful examinees.
